Company Overview of Al Arafa for Investment and Consultancies Company (S.A.E.)



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Al Arafa for Investment and Consultancies Company (S.A.E.) manufactures, retails, distributes, and exports textile and apparel products worldwide. The company offers luxury wear, formal wear, and casual wear for men and kids under the Concrete, Pal Zileri, Ermenegildo Zegna, Massimo Dutti, Zara, Debenhams, Alexander, Racing Green, Suit Direct, Gibson London, Pierre Cardin, and Ben Sherman brands, as well as provides hire services under the Young’s brand. It operates through a network of approximately 40 retail stores under the Concrete brand; 200 Baird stores; and 30 concessions. Al Arafa for Investment and Consultancies Company (S.A.E.) was founded in 1907 and is headquartered in Cairo, Egy...
Al Arafa for Investment and Consultancies Company (S.A.E.) manufactures, retails, distributes, and exports textile and apparel products worldwide. The company offers luxury wear, formal wear, and casual wear for men and kids under the Concrete, Pal Zileri, Ermenegildo Zegna, Massimo Dutti, Zara, Debenhams, Alexander, Racing Green, Suit Direct, Gibson London, Pierre Cardin, and Ben Sherman brands, as well as provides hire services under the Young’s brand. It operates through a network of approximately 40 retail stores under the Concrete brand; 200 Baird stores; and 30 concessions. Al Arafa for Investment and Consultancies Company (S.A.E.) was founded in 1907 and is headquartered in Cairo, Egypt.
Detailed Description


15 Street Near North AreaNasr City Public Free ZoneCairo,  EgyptFounded in 1907



Phone: 20 2 227 310 93

