Al Arafa for Investment and Consultancies Company (S.A.E.) Key Developments

Al Arafa Investment and Consulting Announces Standalone and Consolidated Earnings Results for the Three Months Ended April 30, 2017
Jun 15 17
Al Arafa Investment and Consulting announced standalone and consolidated earnings results for the three months ended April 30, 2017. For the period, on consolidated basis, the company announced net profit of $2,613,954 compared to $1,768,835 a year ago.

For the period, on standalone basis, the company announced net loss of $299,699 compared to net profit of $2,105,791 a year ago.


Al Arafa for Investment and Consultancies Company (S.A.E.), Annual General Meeting, May 14, 2017
Apr 27 17
Al Arafa for Investment and Consultancies Company (S.A.E.), Annual General Meeting, May 14, 2017.


Al Arafa Investment And Consulting Reports Audited Standalone and Consolidated Earnings Results for the Year Ended January 31, 2017
Apr 24 17
Al Arafa Investment And Consulting reported audited standalone and consolidated earnings results for the year ended January 31, 2017. For the year, on standalone basis the company reported net profit was EGP 8,700,318 against loss of EGP 350,991 a year ago.

For the year, on consolidated basis, the company reported net profit was EGP 7,802,760 against EGP 12,452,341 a year ago.


