Business Summary


Provides administrative and restructuring support and holds stakes in textile millsAl Arafa Investment & Consulting operates as a holding company, which engages in the manufacture and trade of textile products.It offers men's and kid's wear, made-to-measure service, and retail stores.The firm distributes its products under the following brand names: Concrete, Pal Zileri, and The Baird Group.The company was founded by Mr. Abdel Ma'assoud Arafa on January 11, 2006 and is headquartered in Cairo, Egypt.
 





